channel.title: NO1 can log onto my server?
channel.description:
I changed my Ip to jakescapeproject.no-ip.biz and I have the DUC v2.2.1 and now nobody can log on . . . When I registered for the no-ip for my server I used my Laptop's IP Address if that helps at all (ns if i was supposed to use the hamachi 1?)
How can I fix this? Oh and do I have to change anything in my source/client files and all that stuff?
Before this gets locked for not being a 'Server Question' Will some1 add a section about whatever you want to call this question? Even though I think its a server question because if no1 can log on to my server how can I even have a server...
